text: Denys Halenkov (; born 13 October 1995) is a professional Ukrainian football striker who plays for Polissya Zhytomyr in the Ukrainian Second League. ==Career== Halenkov is a product of the ISTA Dnipropetrovsk and FC Dnipro Dnipropetrovsk youth school systems. He made his debut for FC Olimpik in the match against FC Illichivets Mariupol on 30 May 2015 in the Ukrainian Premier League. == References == ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:FC Olimpik Donetsk players Category:FC Desna Chernihiv players Category:PFC Sumy players Category:FC Polissya Zhytomyr (2016) players Category:Ukrainian Premier League players Category:Association football forwards Category:Ukrainian Second League players
